  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2><%= image_tag "icon-relax.png", class:"icon" %>Your Storage. Online.</h2>
    <p class="feature">See what's stored, schedule pickups and deliveries of individual items online or from your mobile device. It couldn't be easier.</p>
    <%= link_to "Learn more...", how_it_works_path %>

  </div>
</div>

